{"tid":1259733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣戰］抗爭告白心聲Poster，請廣傳！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T02:34:26.000Z","uid":269585,"like":256,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb5f19c172297ba1dc090517d04081feb3892fc","tid":1259733,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽我講！！</span>  </em><br />\n好多人係616 行完游行之後，都覺得班細路應該要返屋企了，再做落去就係做多左喇。 <br />\n由圍警總果日開始，佢地心入面都同繼續抗爭既人割左蓆。<br />\n而係佢地心目中， 616 後所有野都好似擾民咁，佢地開始覺得&rdquo;唔岩喇&rdquo;、&rdquo;見好就要收喇&rdquo;。<br />\n咁既情況其實會失去部份民心。 <br />\n而來緊既G20習特會令香港近日的抗爭運動進入白熱化，為左令更多人明白認同，<br />\n我地既團隊做左一set poster，向社會上被影響既唔同人士告白。<br />\n希望大眾能理解抗爭者的初心，支持今次運動。<br />\n所以我地今次既Target 係一D 比較中間派，或者616 拎完光環就算既人。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令佢地就算唔支持，都起碼體諒，不唾棄！</span> </strong><br />\n因為我地知道今次運動既一個要點係，兄弟爬山，各自努力！唔好割蓆，大家都為件事好！  <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nObjective ：<br />\n1）要游離份子唔好唾棄繼續堅持既人，要體諒<br />\n2）繼續堅持既人因為別人體諒，民心所向，就自然會更有動力行落去</span></span></strong>  <br />\n<br />\n請大家盡量share 俾D 中間派人士！所有fb group / whatsapp/ wechat....<br />\n拉籠得幾多得幾多！    最後⋯⋯<br />\n！！！！！請廣傳！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCdf8WT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCdf8WT.jpg&h=6d9a12f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbXQdoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbXQdoA.jpg&h=93c6dde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwLNZ3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwLNZ3B.jpg&h=b61af333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRbxrJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRbxrJD.jpg&h=c6fbbac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SAaXQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SAaXQk.jpg&h=b67c58bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdBhCQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdBhCQn.jpg&h=c7fa9002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbEi6JK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbEi6JK.jpg&h=112d2a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ka4rwar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fka4rwar.jpg&h=45a77865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYxTVB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYxTVB8.jpg&h=1b9e2c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7911ebbbc4918a69c3282261bfdd88808824519c","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"推          <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=84d4920a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n未爭取到五項訴求前，<br />\n香港人將「不撤不散」。<br />\n<br />\n五個訴求包括<br />\n1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法&nbsp;<br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動&nbsp;<br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪&nbsp;<br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行&nbsp;<br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/26/232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F26%2F232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png&h=8cfbbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">不撤不退！</div>"},{"pid":"ba1de7771aa6e71fe6a43e615cdce4bbeae25010","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f990304cf79630287915cc24c19f2fe52f3809","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ba64c13141f0b8a2e6cc23bfb46ac0704ea2238","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0fc2cd03fdddf785c491118e1c4ec3450a86eea","tid":1259733,"uid":217844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"痴線好靚"},{"pid":"343f8a192c76881954cffebfeee6dd9e299fb4ca","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6a1f8675e9ce2c41a0c422ab76df9fa270dd907","tid":1259733,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你俾人搶野呀依家<br />\n非法政府代送地呀屌</span><br />\n<br />\n[香港29號割地]  中環海濱割讓俾解放軍完全冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6a6b5d0558923cf8f453ce777bfcd153d863693","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c061766d9534315a0ccc4cce1363d83bafd9f4ee","tid":1259733,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"推