d":20928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48687a700fe4bd1541b68faa40c2fe43a71246b5","tid":1259733,"uid":31778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e53b878f685eaeffa33a73a303b8b3eea87fee1","tid":1259733,"uid":56483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f9b6ccda7841d2042b2c114cabfe3e02d2b57ad","tid":1259733,"uid":269585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13292a734ef1ee511bcc715b37ae4726aea3e928","tid":1259733,"uid":549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"旅客們果張會唔會有外語版?<br />\n因為FOR 旅客既話,用返繁體好似作用不大.."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"因為墨水有限，只能有中文版！<br />\n如果各位巴絲想幫手譯，歡迎提供稿！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"拋磚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWelcome to Hong Kong<br />\nalthough it may not be what you're expecting<br />\n<br />\nWe Hongkonger are working hard in the past few weeks<br />\nto fight for what we treasure and to protect our beloved city.<br />\n<br />\nA little troublesome to you today, but a big step to a better Hong Kong in the future.<br />\n<br />\n#Hongkonger #Nochinaextradition"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Dear Tourists<br />\n           Please excuse the not so lovely Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<br />\n           The series of event happening this month might have ruined your long-planned journey.<br />\n           However, we are doing all we can to preserve the most beautiful side of this city. <br />\n           We wish that when you are back for your next trip, we can present you with a even                       <br />\n           better Hong Kong.<br />\n           <br />\n           From <br />\n           HongKongers who are still fighting #KeepFighting"},{"pid":"320defcaaf352e93f0ff127f546ddf5506df624a","tid":1259733,"uid":263651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"推上熱門!<br />\n屋企人本身616前都支持, 跟著既行動就話D人唔和平搞亂香港開始反對, 再出左建制條5毛鬧父母就更加反對, 雖然成日洗佢腦, 話遊行政府唔理要用其他方法, 佢都聽唔入耳, 希望傳到大家都明抗爭者心聲! 等香港人唔好善忘, 勿忘初衷"},{"pid":"bd043833cb311ef602fe7ddebcd1469f29282718","tid":1259733,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"525c0c435ad950713420b8f2cc551bf27fb952cb","tid":1259733,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30225836480624d24234724d768b912ac9865dc","tid":1259733,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb5f19c172297ba1dc090517d04081feb3892fc","tid":1259733,"uid":269585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽我講！！</span>  </em><br />\n好多人係616 行完游行之後，都覺得班細路應該要返屋企了，再做落去就係做多左喇。 <br />\n由圍警總果日開始，佢地心入面都同繼續抗爭既人割左蓆。<br />\n而係佢地心目中， 616 後所有野都好似擾民咁，佢地開始覺得&rdquo;唔岩喇&rdquo;、&rdquo;見好就要收喇&rdquo;。<br />\n咁既情況其實會失去部份民心。 <br />\n而來緊既G20習特會令香港近日的抗爭運動進入白熱化，為左令更多人明白認同，<br />\n我地既團隊做左一set poster，向社會上被影響既唔同人士告白。<br />\n希望大眾能理解抗爭者的初心，支持今次運動。<br />\n所以我地今次既Target 係一D 比較中間派，或者616 拎完光環就算既人。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令佢地就算唔支持，都起碼體諒，不唾棄！</span> </strong><br />\n因為我地知道今次運動既一個要點係，兄弟爬山，各自努力！唔好割蓆，大家都為件事好！  <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nObjective ：<br />\n1）要游離份子唔好唾棄繼續堅持既人，要體諒<br />\n2）繼續堅持既人因為別人體諒，民心所向，就自然會更有動力行落去</span></span></strong>  <br />\n<br />\n請大家盡量share 俾D 中間派人士！所有fb group / whatsapp/ wechat....<br />\n拉籠得幾多得幾多！    最後⋯⋯<br />\n！！！！！請廣傳！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCdf8WT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCdf8WT.jpg&h=6d9a12f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbXQdoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbXQdoA.jpg&h=93c6dde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwLNZ3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwLNZ3B.jpg&h=b61af333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRbxrJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRbxrJD.jpg&h=c6fbbac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SAaXQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SAaXQk.jpg&h=b67c58bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdBhCQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdBhCQn.jpg&h=c7fa9002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbEi6JK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbEi6JK.jpg&h=112d2a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ka4rwar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fka4rwar.jpg&h=45a77865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYxTVB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYxTVB8.jpg&h=1b9e2c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"好靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感激文宣組"},{"pid":"fac082befef1f361bdc795f064f36c2398967530","tid":1259733,"uid":98672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:41:22.000Z","msg":"好高質，PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b91603530084744e3f9c0942c14f08d371474","tid":1259733,"uid":38182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b01e4af0b7c3