一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=84d4920a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n未爭取到五項訴求前，<br />\n香港人將「不撤不散」。<br />\n<br />\n五個訴求包括<br />\n1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法&nbsp;<br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動&nbsp;<br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪&nbsp;<br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行&nbsp;<br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/26/232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F26%2F232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png&h=8cfbbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">不撤不退！</div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f8e5964f436e53b812bcfa0904e73be7b9222ec","tid":1259733,"uid":20576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20d1d80a9567cd2f61474558e90f78bede552d55","tid":1259733,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef5ec311f63ece46aa97ddd76a393de6462e698f","tid":1259733,"uid":196065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8edc262c883f21ce1d9b7d927fc331307febfc18","tid":1259733,"uid":28399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65e050e5cab9fe8a3d36661f2be7771019b67fab","tid":1259733,"uid":167774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"整得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i