ong><br />\n因為我地知道今次運動既一個要點係，兄弟爬山，各自努力！唔好割蓆，大家都為件事好！  <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nObjective ：<br />\n1）要游離份子唔好唾棄繼續堅持既人，要體諒<br />\n2）繼續堅持既人因為別人體諒，民心所向，就自然會更有動力行落去</span></span></strong>  <br />\n<br />\n請大家盡量share 俾D 中間派人士！所有fb group / whatsapp/ wechat....<br />\n拉籠得幾多得幾多！    最後⋯⋯<br />\n！！！！！請廣傳！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCdf8WT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCdf8WT.jpg&h=6d9a12f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbXQdoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbXQdoA.jpg&h=93c6dde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwLNZ3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwLNZ3B.jpg&h=b61af333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRbxrJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRbxrJD.jpg&h=c6fbbac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SAaXQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SAaXQk.jpg&h=b67c58bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdBhCQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdBhCQn.jpg&h=c7fa9002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbEi6JK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbEi6JK.jpg&h=112d2a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ka4rwar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fka4rwar.jpg&h=45a77865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYxTVB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYxTVB8.jpg&h=1b9e2c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dfed95014dc98a6fa8201e45408f4d8076b1c13","tid":1259733,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201